Class Space

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Space
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Space
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Space's whole purpose is store a lot of the data on the car as well as the values that have been selected at the time of check in. Most of this gets reset with each car removal.
    Author:
    Matt Guidi

    • Field Detail

      • TIME_MODIFIER

        public static final long TIME_MODIFIER
        This time modifier helps us modify the "real-time" used to calculate our close time.
        It helps make cost approximation and testing a lot easier
        Use 3,600,000 for 1 millisecond to equal one hour
        Use 60,000 for 1 millisecond to equal one minute
        Use 1,000 for 1 millisecond to equal one second
        Use 1 for normal time.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
